Class SRHitHspImplem

  • java.lang.Object
    • bzh.plealog.bioinfo.api.data.searchresult.utils.SRHitHspImplem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SRHitHSP

    public class SRHitHspImplem
extends Object
implements SRHitHSP
    This interface defines a container for a Blast Hit. This is a utility class used in the GUI of KLblaster to display a particular HSP contained in a particuler Hit.
    Author:
    Patrick G. Durand

      • SRHitHspImplem

        public SRHitHspImplem(SRHit hit,
              String bc,
              int hspNum,
              int qSize,
              int bType)
        Creates a BlastHitHsp.
        Parameters:
        hit - the hit containing the HSP to display
        bc - the BlastClient that produced this BlastHitHsp
        hspNum - the HSP to display, identified by its order number within the Hit
        qSize - the query size
        bType - the Blast type, one of BOutput.BLASTXXX integer constants
